# Implementation Plan: System Context Activity Log

## Goal Description
The user requires a structured history of all agent activities within the [SystemContext](file:///c:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/scratch/AXON-boilerplate/src/types/agent_types.ts#122-131). This history must pair the **Input/Decision** (Configuration, Directive) with the **Output/Data** (Result, Artifact) to allow full traceability of the "Question/Answer" cycle.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change expands the [SystemContext](file:///c:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/scratch/AXON-boilerplate/src/types/agent_types.ts#122-131) object. All components reading from Context will now have access to the full `activity_log`.

